{"tid":1315441,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"反轉！西媒曝J.洛不去意甲轉投馬體會","createTime":"2019-07-14T14:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T16:21:12.000Z","uid":34571,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"52ea1cfcd16b1b82172469d35dd52b0dd412150b","tid":1315441,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:00:04.000Z","msg":"此前J.洛已經非常接近加盟拿玻里，不過《馬卡報》的最新消息卻表示，這筆交易很有可能會出現變數，J.洛有可能會轉會馬體會。雖然這聽上去很聳人聽聞，但這真的有可能發生。<br />\n<br />\n  J.洛不想離開馬德里這座城市，而馬體會也十分有意簽下這名強援，J洛賓人現在也跟更加傾向於加盟馬體會。馬體會十分接近簽下J.洛，目前唯一的阻礙，就是等待皇馬的同意。儘管此前看上去J.洛去拿玻里已經是已經決定的事情了，但J.洛考慮到自己的利益，他決心推動轉會馬體會的進度。<br />\n<br />\n  J.洛並不在施丹的計劃之中，過去兩個賽季他是在拜仁度過的，而皇馬已經決定在今夏將他賣掉。<br />\n<br />\n祖奧菲力斯<br />\n莫拉達<br />\n占士<br />\nMarcos Llorente<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7e6cc5e88f0e2848f0d90b7fc2a8e7ca000611","tid":1315441,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd12bc4ea3c365fa5b21f890422786980fbdec60","tid":1315441,"uid":165817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:41:41.000Z","msg":"樓主講嗰四個 有三個都係ex皇馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就嚟fd過AC米蘭同國際米蘭"},{"pid":"b9f777679d8b020c24b4af6035ff79a673f167ea","tid":1315441,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:42:39.000Z","msg":"James用下體會應豪改善到組織力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbb9daf198fa655cc7c312aa23ff56368c683fd","tid":1315441,"uid":165817,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid"